>Talism&aacute;n, magia blanca de origen alqu&iacute;mico.</p>"},"_stats":{"systemId":"sandbox","systemVersion":"0.14.0(RC7)","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1681232036271,"modifiedTime":1681232990124,"lastModifiedBy":"NLu8dzFBI3Kvrwky"},"_id":"SqmapNEqHJ69RqRQ","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"NLu8dzFBI3Kvrwky":3}}
